  "proposal": {
    "title": "Add Specs: Dash",
    "description": "Adding new specification support for relaying Dash data on Lava. Dash-native ChainLock/InstantSend, masternode/quorum/ProTx (Evo), governance/CoinJoin-info and special-transaction reads are added on top of the imported BTC Bitcoin-Core RPC surface; the address/spent/timestamp-index reads require a node started with -addressindex/-spentindex/-timestampindex.",
